c=0
for i in list(data):
    if len(data[i].unique())<=6:
        data[i]=data[i].astype('category')
        c+=1
data['dm_pt']=data['dm_pt'].astype('int')
data['DMstatus']=data['DMstatus'].astype('int')
In [9]:
data_1=data[:][data['DMstatus']==1].reset_index(drop=True)
train_1=data_1.sample(frac=0.8,random_state=123)
train_re_1=data_1.drop(train_1.index)
test_1=train_re_1.sample(frac=0.5,random_state=123)
validation_1=train_re_1.drop(test_1.index)

data_0=data[:][data['DMstatus']==0].reset_index(drop=True)
train_0=data_0.sample(frac=0.8,random_state=123)
train_re_0=data_0.drop(train_0.index)
test_0=train_re_0.sample(frac=0.5,random_state=123)
validation_0=train_re_0.drop(test_0.index)

train=pd.concat([train_0,train_1]).sample(frac=1,random_state=123)
test=pd.concat([test_0,test_1]).sample(frac=1,random_state=123)
validation=pd.concat([validation_0,validation_1]).sample(frac=1,random_state=123)

train.reset_index(drop=True, inplace=True)
test.reset_index(drop=True, inplace=True)
validation.reset_index(drop=True, inplace=True)

In [27]:
train_lgb = lgb.Dataset(train_x, label = train_y_status) 
test_lgb = lgb.Dataset(test_x, label = test_y_status) 

# param  
learning_rate_list=[0.1,0.01]
max_depth_list=[1,10,30]
num_leaves_list=[10,23+36]
feature_fraction_list=[0.7,1.0]
bagging_fraction_list=[0.7,1.0]
num_iterations_list=[10,50,100]
lambda_l1_list=[0,0.1]
lambda_l2_list=[0,0.1]


param_list=pd.DataFrame({'learning_rate':[],'max_depth':[],'num_leaves':[],'feature_fraction':[],'bagging_fraction':[],'num_iterations':[],'lambda_l1':[],'lambda_l2':[], 'AUC':[] })

for a in learning_rate_list:
    for b in max_depth_list:
        for c in num_leaves_list:
            for d in feature_fraction_list:
                for e in bagging_fraction_list:
                    for f in num_iterations_list:
                        for g in lambda_l1_list:
                            for h in lambda_l2_list:
                                params = {'learning_rate': a, 
                                            'max_depth': b,
                                            'boosting': 'gbdt', 
                                            'objective': 'binary', 
                                            'metric': 'auc',
                                            'is_training_metric': True, 
                                            'num_leaves': c, 
                                            'feature_fraction': d, 
                                            'bagging_fraction': e,
                                            'lambda_l1':g,
                                            'lambda_l2':h
                                            }
                                model = lgb.train(params, train_lgb, f, test_lgb, verbose_eval=10, early_stopping_rounds=10)
                                param_list = param_list.append(pd.Series([a,b,c,d,e,f,g,h,roc_auc_score(test_y_status, model.predict(test_x))], index=param_list.columns), ignore_index=True)
param_list=param_list.sort_values(by=['AUC'], axis=0, ascending=False)
param_list.reset_index(drop=True,inplace=True)
params = {'learning_rate':  float(param_list['learning_rate'][0]),
          'max_depth': int(param_list['max_depth'][0]),
          'boosting': 'gbdt',
          'objective': 'binary', 
          'metric': 'auc',
          'is_training_metric': True, 
          'num_leaves': int(param_list['num_leaves'][0]), 
          'feature_fraction': float(param_list['feature_fraction'][0]), 
          'bagging_fraction': float(param_list['bagging_fraction'][0]), 
          'lambda_l1': float(param_list['lambda_l1'][0]),
          'lambda_l2': float(param_list['lambda_l2'][0]), 
          }
model = lgb.train(params, train_lgb, int(param_list['num_iterations'][0]), test_lgb,  verbose_eval=10, early_stopping_rounds=10)
predict_test = model.predict(test_x)
predict_test_df = pd.DataFrame(predict_test)

plt.title('Receiver Operating Characteristic')

fpr, tpr, threshold = metrics.roc_curve(test_y_status, predict_test_df)
roc_auc = metrics.auc(fpr, tpr)
plt.plot(fpr, tpr, 'r--', label = 'DMstatus prediction performance from test = %0.4f' % roc_auc)

plt.legend(loc = 'lower right')
plt.plot([0, 1], [0, 1],'k--')
plt.xlim([0, 1])
plt.ylim([0, 1])
plt.ylabel('True Positive Rate')
plt.xlabel('False Positive Rate')
plt.savefig('ROC_CURVE_test.jpg', dpi=500)
plt.show()


predict_validation = model.predict(validation_x)
predict_validation_df = pd.DataFrame(predict_validation)
joblib.dump(model, 'model.pkl') 

#ROC cureve 

plt.title('Receiver Operating Characteristic')

fpr, tpr, threshold = metrics.roc_curve(validation_y_status, predict_validation_df)
roc_auc = metrics.auc(fpr, tpr)
plt.plot(fpr, tpr, 'r--', label = 'DMstatus prediction performance from validation = %0.4f' % roc_auc)

plt.legend(loc = 'lower right')
plt.plot([0, 1], [0, 1],'k--')
plt.xlim([0, 1])
plt.ylim([0, 1])
plt.ylabel('True Positive Rate')
plt.xlabel('False Positive Rate')
plt.savefig('ROC_CURVE_validation.jpg', dpi=500)
plt.show()

In [29]:
train_lgb = lgb.Dataset(train_x, label = train_y_status) 
test_lgb = lgb.Dataset(test_x, label = test_y_status) 

# param  
learning_rate_list=[0.05,0.01]
max_depth_list=[1,10,30]
num_leaves_list=[23+36]
feature_fraction_list=[0.7,1.0]
bagging_fraction_list=[0.7,1.0]
num_iterations_list=[10,50,100]
lambda_l1_list=[0,0.1]
lambda_l2_list=[0,0.1]


param_list=pd.DataFrame({'learning_rate':[],'max_depth':[],'num_leaves':[],'feature_fraction':[],'bagging_fraction':[],'num_iterations':[],'lambda_l1':[],'lambda_l2':[], 'AUC':[] })

for a in learning_rate_list:
    for b in max_depth_list:
        for c in num_leaves_list:
            for d in feature_fraction_list:
                for e in bagging_fraction_list:
                    for f in num_iterations_list:
                        for g in lambda_l1_list:
                            for h in lambda_l2_list:
                                params = {'learning_rate': a, 
                                            'max_depth': b,
                                            'boosting': 'gbdt', 
                                            'objective': 'binary', 
                                            'metric': 'auc',
                                            'is_training_metric': True, 
                                            'num_leaves': c, 
                                            'feature_fraction': d, 
                                            'bagging_fraction': e,
                                            'lambda_l1':g,
                                            'lambda_l2':h
                                            }
                                model = lgb.train(params, train_lgb, f, test_lgb, verbose_eval=10, early_stopping_rounds=10)
                                param_list = param_list.append(pd.Series([a,b,c,d,e,f,g,h,roc_auc_score(test_y_status, model.predict(test_x))], index=param_list.columns), ignore_index=True)
param_list=param_list.sort_values(by=['AUC'], axis=0, ascending=False)
param_list.reset_index(drop=True,inplace=True)
params = {'learning_rate':  float(param_list['learning_rate'][0]),
          'max_depth': int(param_list['max_depth'][0]),
          'boosting': 'gbdt',
          'objective': 'binary', 
          'metric': 'auc',
          'is_training_metric': True, 
          'num_leaves': int(param_list['num_leaves'][0]), 
          'feature_fraction': float(param_list['feature_fraction'][0]), 
          'bagging_fraction': float(param_list['bagging_fraction'][0]), 
          'lambda_l1': float(param_list['lambda_l1'][0]),
          'lambda_l2': float(param_list['lambda_l2'][0]), 
          }
model = lgb.train(params, train_lgb, int(param_list['num_iterations'][0]), test_lgb,  verbose_eval=10, early_stopping_rounds=10)
predict_test = model.predict(test_x)
predict_test_df = pd.DataFrame(predict_test)

plt.title('Receiver Operating Characteristic')

fpr, tpr, threshold = metrics.roc_curve(test_y_status, predict_test_df)
roc_auc = metrics.auc(fpr, tpr)
plt.plot(fpr, tpr, 'r--', label = 'DMstatus prediction performance from test = %0.4f' % roc_auc)

plt.legend(loc = 'lower right')
plt.plot([0, 1], [0, 1],'k--')
plt.xlim([0, 1])
plt.ylim([0, 1])
plt.ylabel('True Positive Rate')
plt.xlabel('False Positive Rate')
plt.savefig('ROC_CURVE_test.jpg', dpi=500)
plt.show()


predict_validation = model.predict(validation_x)
predict_validation_df = pd.DataFrame(predict_validation)
joblib.dump(model, 'model.pkl')

In [32]:
train_lgb = lgb.Dataset(train_x, label = train_y_pt) 
test_lgb = lgb.Dataset(test_x, label = test_y_pt) 

# param  
learning_rate_list=[0.1,0.01]
max_depth_list=[10,30]
num_leaves_list=[10,23+36,100]
feature_fraction_list=[0.7,1.0]
bagging_fraction_list=[0.7,1.0]
num_iterations_list=[50,100,1000]

param_list=pd.DataFrame({'learning_rate':[],'max_depth':[],'num_leaves':[],'feature_fraction':[],'bagging_fraction':[],'num_iterations':[], 'mse':[] })

for a in learning_rate_list:
    for b in max_depth_list:
        for c in num_leaves_list:
            for d in feature_fraction_list:
                for e in bagging_fraction_list:
                    for f in num_iterations_list:
                        params = {'learning_rate': a, 
                                    'max_depth': b,
                                    'boosting': 'gbdt', 
                                    'objective': 'regression', 
                                    'metric': 'mse',
                                    'is_training_metric': True, 
                                    'num_leaves': c, 
                                    'feature_fraction': d, 
                                    'bagging_fraction': e, 
                                    }
                        model = lgb.train(params, train_lgb, f, test_lgb, verbose_eval=100, early_stopping_rounds=100)
                        param_list = param_list.append(pd.Series([a,b,c,d,e,f,mean_squared_error(test_y_pt, model.predict(test_x))], index=param_list.columns), ignore_index=True)
param_list=param_list.sort_values(by=['mse'], axis=0, ascending=True)
param_list.reset_index(drop=True,inplace=True)
params = {'learning_rate':  float(param_list['learning_rate'][0]),
          'max_depth': int(param_list['max_depth'][0]),
          'boosting': 'gbdt',
          'objective': 'regression', 
          'metric': 'mse',
          'is_training_metric': True, 
          'num_leaves': int(param_list['num_leaves'][0]), 
          'feature_fraction': float(param_list['feature_fraction'][0]), 
          'bagging_fraction': float(param_list['bagging_fraction'][0]), 
          }
model = lgb.train(params, train_lgb, int(param_list['num_iterations'][0]), test_lgb,  verbose_eval=100, early_stopping_rounds=100)
joblib.dump(model, 'model.pkl') 
predict_test = model.predict(test_x)
predict_test_df = pd.DataFrame(predict_test)

categorical_feature in param dict is overridden.
